title: Jimmy's Taste of Florida
overview: Join Jimmy Doherty as he embarks on a culinary tour of Florida. From the historic neighbourhoods of Pensacola to the vibrant streets of Miami, Jimmy unveils the state's eclectic food culture.A tapestry of Latin American, Caribbean and Southern influences to name a few! Florida sets the stage for Jimmy's culinary exploration. With its sun-kissed beaches, lush landscapes and a subtropical climate, the state becomes a canvas for flavours as vibrant as its surroundings.
